title: Diamond Beveling Chamfer Bits 0-50MM - Diamond Cone Tile Bits for Chamfering Enlarging Shaping Trimming Exsiting Holes in Ceramic Porcelain Tile Marble Granite M14 Thread for Angle Grinder LEKOMESH
features: 【Size】Diameter: 0-50MM, Total length: 55mm, Working Depth: 46mm, M14 Thread, Grit: #80/100, Chamfer Angle: Top Angle 60 degree.
【Multi-function】Used for chamfering, reaming, grinding and polishing exsiting holes in Ceramic Porcelain Tile Marble Granite Artificial Stone and Stoneware etc. Dry or Wet Use.

【Special Design & Save Money】Inclined Angle and Vacuum Brazed Technology provide flat and fast smooth reaming with high grinding speed. With just one standard core bit and this finger bit you are able to create many different hole sizes.
【Premium Material】High quality diamond covers the working face with Grit#80/100, which is strong and durable. Provides higher processing efficiency and longer service life.

【Recommended Machine】: Fit on M14 Thread angle grinders. Recommended RPM: 6000, maximum RPM: 11000. If you want to fit it on drills or other machine, you need an adapter, such as SDS, Hex, Round Plus Shank. The diamond bit can NOT BE USED TO DRILL HOLES.
